Assignment 1: Lorenz Attractor

Evan Brookens
CSCI4229 Fall 2014

Displays Lorenz Attractor in a 3D space

Key bindings
  S 	 Make sigma's data grow begining at 10
  s      Make sigma's data decrease
  B 	 Make beta's data grow begining at 2
  b 	 Make beta's data decrease
  R 	 Make rho's data grow: beings at 20
  r 	 Make rho's data decrease
  arrows Change view angle
  0      Reset view angle
  ESC    Exit

Time to complete this assignment: 4hrs 